snippet.title: Spill the Beans - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
A secret recipe has been stolen and you’re tasked with finding the culprit…trouble is, you’re the one whodunnit.

Investigate, interrogate and manipulate your way to framing the perfect scapegoat in this modern fantasy reverse detective visual novel.

When you’re the one whodunnit, who will you get to Spill The Beans?

Developed by Skeletal Games.
